about.summary: C decoder/encoder routines for GRIB edition 2.

name: g2clib
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.6.0" %}

package:
    name: g2clib
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: g2clib-{{ version }}.tar
    url: http://www.nco.ncep.noaa.gov/pmb/codes/GRIB2/g2clib-{{ version }}.tar
    sha256: afec1ea29979b84369d0f46f305ed12f73f1450ec2db737664ec7f75c1163add

build:
    number: 0
    skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
    build:
        - libpng >=1.6.21,<1.7
        - zlib 1.2.*
        - jasper
    run:
        - libpng >=1.6.21,<1.7
        - zlib 1.2.*
        - jasper

test:
    commands:
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libg2c_v1.6.0.a  # [unix]
        - conda inspect linkages -n _test g2clib  # [not win]
        - conda inspect objects -n _test g2clib  # [osx]

about:
    home: http://www.nco.ncep.noaa.gov/pmb/codes/GRIB2/
    license: Public Domain
    summary: 'C decoder/encoder routines for GRIB edition 2.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
        - jhamman
